                    "body": "I'm not sure we support memory sizes this small. However, if we don't support it, then we need to fail when starting the plasma store in the first place instead of letting it fail later.\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\nThis issue probably has to do with the default malloc sizes in this file\u00a0\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/apache/arrow/blob/d48dce2cfebdbd044a8260d0a77f5fe3d89a4a2d/cpp/src/plasma/malloc.cc#L47",
